<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/1089071-i-m-on-page-136-at-the-moment-just-as">I&#39;m on page 136 at the moment, just as Taffy 3&#39;s TBM Avengers are finding Kurita&#39;s Middle Force. Question, I&#39;ve gone back and re-read a couple of times, but just to be certain, Sprague and Taffy 3 et al are under the impression that Task Force 34 is there to defend them? But Halsey has actually called them north to engage Ozawa&#39;s Northern Force, correct?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_1089071'><a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F5400.The_Last_Stand_of_the_Tin_Can_Sailors">like</a></span>

