<div class='allCommunityAnswers'>
<div class='communityAnswer'>
<div class='communityAnswerBody'>
<div class='answererUserIcon'>
<a class="leftAlignedImage userPhoto" href="/user/show/30463792-sameer"><img alt="" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/users/1533311921i/30463792._UX100_CR0,0,100,100_.jpg" /></a>
</div>
<div class='communityAnswerTextContainer'>
<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/30463792-sameer">Sameer</a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<div class='spoiler'>
This answer contains spoilers…
<span class='spoilerAnswerText'>
<a class="jsShowSpoiler spoilerAction">(view spoiler)</a><span class="spoilerContainer" style="display: none">[
  
    Task Force 34 existed only on paper. It never was created based on the battleships under Admiral W. Lee. Halsey didn't think it was needed. <br /><br />Main reaso<a href="#" rel="nofollow noopener">…more</a>
    Task Force 34 existed only on paper. It never was created based on the battleships under Admiral W. Lee. Halsey didn't think it was needed. <br /><br />Main reason for him not wanting it to be formed was that, he was on one of the battleships. He would have been forced to send his carriers without him to North, had the task force been formed.<br /><br />You might want to know about <br /><a target="_blank" href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_world_wonders" rel="nofollow noopener">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_wor...</a><a href="#" rel="nofollow noopener">(less)</a>
  
 <a class="jsHideSpoiler spoilerAction">(hide spoiler)</a>]</span>
</span>
</div>
</span>
