          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1174288245" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer9427931430530796160">The Battle of Leyte Gulf is by far the greatest example of David vs. Goliath. David of course wins the day. Goliath is badly mauled and retreats to Iwo Jima and Okinawa. The battle illustrates the desparate gamble of destroyers against the entire IJN Center Force. I can only imagine the sickening feeling the sailors had when the pagoda style masts of battleships and cruisers came over the horizon. I only wish there was more included from the Japanese side of the battle. A great book.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


