<li class='cover' id='bookCover_11472008'>
<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/11472008-the-battle-of-midway"><img alt="The Battle of Midway" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1348765939l/11472008._SX98_.jpg" />
