<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/1312031.The_Longest_Winter"><img alt="The Longest Winter: The Battle of the Bulge and the Epic Story of World War II&#39;s Most Decorated Platoon" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1387740265l/1312031._SX98_.jpg" />
